    "_comment": "Waypoint coordinates in the SLAM map frame (metres). All entries below are PLACEHOLDERS (0,0,0,1) — see _calibration_protocol for how to fill them. Only Ground Floor waypoints are listed; AI-SHA cannot reach the First Floor (Zone 6) without elevator support.",
    "_calibration_protocol": [
        "1. Generate SLAM map: ros2 launch aisha_integration rpi_launch.py enable_slam:=true",
        "2. Drive robot through campus via teleop, save map:",
        "     ros2 run nav2_map_server map_saver_cli -f ~/maps/iscshj_campus",
        "3. Load map in RViz: ros2 launch nav2_bringup bringup_launch.py map:=~/maps/iscshj_campus.yaml",
        "4. Drive robot to each location, then record pose:",
        "     ros2 topic echo /amcl_pose --once",
        "5. Copy position.x, position.y, orientation.z, orientation.w into this file.",
        "6. Test: ros2 topic pub /nav_goal std_msgs/String '{data: \"cafeteria\"}' --once"
